          </h1>
          <div>
            <div class="intro__photo"></div>
            <ul class="intro__social">
              <li>
                <a
                  href="mailto:rinaldopasa97@gmail.com?subject=Hello There!&body=Hi Rinaldo, so I was looking at your portfolio and..."
                >
                  <figure>
                    <img src="/google.svg" alt="" width="24" height="24" />
